                <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Iulius z<supplied reason="lost">aconus! et</supplied> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Aurel</abbr><ex>ia</ex></expan> Ia<supplied reason="lost">nuaria con</supplied><lb break="no" n="3"/>iux eius h<supplied reason="lost">oc! sarcofa</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/>gum <note>sic</note> sibi <supplied reason="lost">vibi! posuerunt</supplied> <lb n="5"/>si quis pos<supplied reason="lost">t nostram pau</supplied><lb break="no" n="6"/>sationem <supplied reason="lost">hoc! sarcofa</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"/>gum <note>sic</note> ape<supplied reason="lost">rire voluerit in</supplied><lb break="no" n="8"/>ferit aec<expan><ex>c</ex><abbr>l</abbr></expan><supplied reason="lost">esiae! <expan><abbr>Salon</abbr><ex>itanae</ex></expan> ar</supplied><lb break="no" n="9"/>genti libr<supplied reason="lost">as quinquaginta</supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>Dep</abbr><ex>ositio</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">Iuli</supplied> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">zaco</supplied><lb break="no" n="4"/><supplied reason="lost">nis!</supplied> <lb n="5"/><supplied reason="lost">die</supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">IIII</supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">Nonas</supplied> <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost">Novem</supplied><lb break="no" n="9"/><supplied reason="lost">bres</supplied> <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="lost">Datia</supplied><lb break="no" n="11"/><supplied reason="lost">no et</supplied> <lb n="12"/><supplied reason="lost">Cerea</supplied><lb break="no" n="13"/><supplied reason="lost">le</supplied> <lb n="14"/><supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>co</abbr><ex>n</ex><abbr>ss</abbr><ex>ulibus</ex></expan></supplied>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Sarkophagkasten. Inschriftfeld auf der Vorderseite in Form einer tabula ansata; die andere Inschrift befand sich auf der linken Nebenseite. Inschrifttext weitgehend nur handschriftlich überliefert; ein Fragment der Vorderseite im Jahr 2001 in der Kathedrale S. Domninus vermauert wiedergefunden; Maßangaben beziehen sich auf dieses Fragment. Z. 8 (Ende): hedera vor AR. (B): CIL III 2654. 8652; ILS 8254; ILCV 1223; Marin u. a.: Abweichungen in der Textwiedergabe.</p>
            </div>
